1125
00:58:41,897 --> 00:58:43,382


1126
00:58:43,482 --> 00:58:47,978
...five, four, three, two,

1127
00:58:48,146 --> 00:58:50,222
one, bingo!

1128
00:58:50,322 --> 00:58:51,932
We made it! Close the door, Eustace!
We made it.

1129
00:58:52,032 --> 00:58:54,935
Look, look, we're still in business.
We've still got 2 bucks left.

1130
00:58:55,035 --> 00:58:56,854
Look, let's have some of that.
Let's celebrate!

1131
00:58:56,954 --> 00:58:58,355
Get some glasses, Tilly.

1132
00:58:58,455 --> 00:59:01,692
- Well, a couple of financial wizards.
- Call us Rockefellers.

1133
00:59:01,792 --> 00:59:04,278
Get a tray for these two
great big important simoleons here.

1134
00:59:04,378 --> 00:59:05,905
