Well, come on, George.
Come on downstairs, quick.

2212
02:05:01,381 --> 02:05:02,700
- They're on their way.
- All right.

2213
02:05:02,800 --> 02:05:04,042
Come on.

2214
02:05:06,421 --> 02:05:08,213
Come on in here now.

2215
02:05:09,382 --> 02:05:11,000
Now, you stand right over here
by the tree.

2216
02:05:11,100 --> 02:05:13,335
Right there, and don't move.
Don't move.

2217
02:05:13,435 --> 02:05:15,012
